text: Qubo is a children's TV channel by Ion Media. Qubo may also refer to: * Fiat Qubo, a compact MPV based on the Fiat Fiorno * Quadratic unconstrained binary optimization (QUBO), a pattern matching technique common in machine learning applications ==See also== * Qu Bo (disambiguation) * Qubo Saeed Khan, a city in Sindh province, Pakistan
title: Qubo (disambiguation)
